<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="vi">

<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Dashboard - Cửa hàng 24h</title>
  <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/bootstrap@5.3.2/dist/css/bootstrap.min.css" rel="stylesheet">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
  <style>
    body {
      min-height: 100vh;
      background: linear-gradient(135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%);
      font-family: 'Segoe UI', sans-serif;
    }

    .sidebar {
      position: fixed;
      top: 0;
      left: 0;
      height: 100vh;
      width: 280px;
      background: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.7);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      color: white;
      padding-top: 2rem;
      z-index: 1000;
    }

    .sidebar .logo {
      text-align: center;
      margin-bottom: 3rem;
      font-size: 1.8rem;
      font-weight: 700;
    }

    .sidebar .nav-link {
      color: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.8);
      padding: 0.9rem 1.5rem;
      border-radius: 0 50px 50px 0;
      margin: 0.3rem 1rem;
      transition: all 0.3s;
    }

    .sidebar .nav-link:hover {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.2);
      color: white;
      margin-left: 0.5rem;
    }

    .content {
      margin-left: 280px;
      padding: 2rem;
      min-height: 100vh;
    }

    .glass-card {
      background: rgba(255, 255, 255, 0.95);
      border-radius: 20px;
      box-shadow: 0 15px 35px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.2);
      backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
      padding: 3rem;
      text-align: center;
    }

    .welcome-icon {
      font-size: 5rem;
      color: #667eea;
      margin-bottom: 1.5rem;
    }

    @media (max-width: 992px) {
      .sidebar {
        width: 80px;
      }

      .sidebar .logo span,
      .sidebar .nav-text {
        display: none;
      }

      .content {
        margin-left: 80px;
      }
    }
  </style>
</head>

<body>
  <div class="sidebar">
    <div class="logo" style="cursor: pointer;" onclick="window.location.href='/dashboard'">
      <i class="fas fa-store-alt fa-2x"></i><span> 24H Store</span>
    </div>
    <nav class="nav flex-column">
      <a class="nav-link" href="/dashboard"><i class="fas fa-home fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Trang
          chủ</span></a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="/products"><i class="fas fa-box fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Sản
          phẩm</span></a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="/inventory"><i class="fas fa-warehouse fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Tồn
          kho</span></a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="/employees"><i class="fas fa-users-cog fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Nhân
          viên</span></a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="/sales"><i class="fas fa-cash-register fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Bán
          hàng</span></a>
      <a class="nav-link" href="/reports"><i class="fas fa-chart-bar fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Báo
          cáo</span></a>
      <hr class="my-4 opacity-50">
      <a class="nav-link text-danger" href="/"><i class="fas fa-sign-out-alt fa-lg me-3"></i><span class="nav-text">Đăng
          xuất</span></a>
    </nav>
  </div>

  <div class="content">
    <div class="glass-card">
      <i class="fas fa-tachometer-alt welcome-icon"></i>
      <h1 class="display-4 text-primary mb-4">Chào mừng đến với hệ thống!</h1>
      <h3>Xin chào <strong>
          <%= typeof username !=='undefined' ? username : 'Guest' %>
        </strong> (<%= typeof role !=='undefined' ? role.toUpperCase() : 'STAFF' %>)</h3>
      <p class="lead mt-4">Hệ thống quản lý cửa hàng 24h đã sẵn sàng. Hãy chọn chức năng từ menu bên trái để bắt đầu.
      </p>
      <hr class="my-5">
      <div class="row text-center">
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <i class="fas fa-box fa-3x text-primary mb-3"></i>
          <h5>Quản lý sản phẩm & tồn kho</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <i class="fas fa-cash-register fa-3x text-success mb-3"></i>
          <h5>Lập hóa đơn bán hàng</h5>
        </div>
        <div class="col-md-4">
          <i class="fas fa-chart-bar fa-3x text-info mb-3"></i>
          <h5>Xem báo cáo doanh thu</h5>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>

</html>